00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:35.119
I think it's just the key because it's too, it really is past the point.

00:09:35.119 --> 00:09:39.239
Anyone person can keep it all on their head and it's very easy to

00:09:39.239 --> 00:09:44.080
accidentally introduce inconsistencies because it's, it's, it's, it's, it's

00:09:44.080 --> 00:09:49.039
